        Attitude Statements For Phone Survey
	(Questions: 9.5, 11.5, 12.10)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. I call long distance only when absolutely necessary.
2. A person can save a lot of money by having only one telephone.
3. Having more than one telephone is well worth the additional cost.
4. My average phone bill is probably smaller than those of most of my friends.
5. Having more than one telephone is a waste of money unless you have a very
   large home.
6. When acquiring a telephone it is important to get the best model even though
   it is more expensive.
